[This moderator regrets this misunderstanding and the archived report will
be amended accordingly. I have to confess that I was not aware at the time
that A(H1N1)v is now the official WHO designation for the new influenza
A(H1N1) pandemic strain. This abbreviation has not been in general use and
perhaps my error will help to make this new designation generally known. -
Mod.CP]
